      <p>=E2=80=8B=E2=80=8B=E2=80=8B=E2=80=8B=E2=80=8B=E2=80=8B=E2=80=8B=E2=
=80=8B=E2=80=8B=E2=80=8B=E2=80=8B=E2=80=8B=E2=80=8B=E2=80=8BTo calculate yo=
ur GPA at Dallas College, you will review the grade point value with the at=
tempted hours.</p>
<p>Y=E2=80=8Bour GPA is calculated by your grade point value:</p>
<ul>
<li>A =3D 4 points per credit hour.=E2=80=8B</li>
<li>B =3D 3 points per credit hour.</li>
<li>C =3D 2 points per credit hour.</li>
<li>D =3D 1 point per credit hour.</li>
<li>F/WF =3D 0 points per credit hour.</li>
</ul>
<p>To calculate your GPA:</p>
<ol>
<li>Multiply hours attempted by the grade value earned for each class.</li>
<li>Total your number of grade points.</li>
<li>Divide total points by total of all your attempted hours.</li>
<li>That's your GPA.</li>
</ol>
